episodes.title: The Kingdom or Cult of Kubala?
episodes.description:
Today we're looking at the "Kingdom of Kubala", a self titled lost African tribe returning to reclaim their stolen ancestral home on the Scottish border. All things considered, I can't help but worry this is a religious cult crafted by an egotistical man for the purpose of having a second wife who's required to do all the housework...
